<item>
            <title>[SPR-7492] NullPointerException during Autowiring a Bean defined in XML and referenced in @Configuration</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-7492</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have configuration in XML files, @Configuration files and component scanning files. While deploying I am getting NullPointerException. The code works fine with XMLs only.&lt;br/&gt;
The stacktrace and code could be found at the Spring Forum reference. I will be glad to attach more if necessary, just let me know.&lt;br/&gt;
With all due respect, the JavaConfig part of the reference manual could be better. It illustrates only simple examples and there are no sample applications available.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
